		<!-- message -->
		<div>Few things I always thought might be good would be,<br />
<br />
a Natural Durability line of AAs for your mana pool rather than your HP pool.<br />
<br />
a burst discipline AA line which reduces your cast time down to 1 second (or insta-cast) and the recast delay to 1 second. Sort of like the FD line of AAs but to speed up your nukes rather than make them boomier and without the extra mana cost per cast. An FD-like recast time or something might be nice.<br />
<br />
a resistance discipline AA line which gives a +decently_noticable modifier to your nukes while it's active. FD-like recast timer and duration. Would be handy for the events which are pure resistance fests.<br />
<br />
a line of ice/magic/fire AAs which provides a third modifier focus to nukes. Say 10 levels of each with each level adding 2% or so to your nukes (random guesses at numbers). Possibly even corresponding lines which adds a mana cost reduction to work with mana preservation items.<br />
<br />
a line of AAs to reduce the Harvest of Druzzil AA's recast time and to increase the amount of mana returned. That or a new flavour HoD which gives more mana but can be used alongside HoD and harvest.<br />
<br />
a 0-mana nuke with a short recast delay and not much damage (200-400 base damage guessing) but allows us to keep pumping out something when mana's short or waiting for a chance to med.<br />
<br />
Think that's all my random musings.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
